# Design Systems A/B

## System A — Soft Gift (`data-theme="gift"`)

Pink `#FF6B9D`, soft bg `#FFF3F8`, heading `#2D2640` · Fonts: Fraunces + Plus Jakarta Sans · Soft rounded cards/pills · Used for storefront, blog public UI, commerce admin dense family.

## System B — Creator (`data-theme="creator"`)

Forest/cream/terracotta HSL tokens · Fonts: Playfair Display + Manrope · Tetris marketing / dense dashboards · Never pink gift tokens.

## Never

Mix themes · treat medical specialists as marketplace creators · Inter/Roboto brand stacks · emoji icons · purple-glow SaaS heroes · hero sticker overlays.

Critical controls need `data-testid` (kebab-case). Tap targets ≥ 48px.

Motion: GSAP primary on Soft Gift storytelling surfaces — see `15-gsap-motion.mdc`. Calm premium, not bounce spam.
